Subject: [PATCH] ath10k: Setup the msa resources before qmi init
Git-commit: 727fec790ead3d75e2735f66209949c2163523ea
Patch-mainline: v5.8-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-13430

Move the msa resources setup out of qmi init and
setup the msa resources as a part of probe before
the qmi init is done.

Tested HW: WCN3990
Tested FW: WLAN.HL.3.1-01040-QCAHLSWMTPLZ-1

Signed-off-by: Rakesh Pillai <pillair@codeaurora.org>
